司。 企查查 App 显示，2017 年 7 月，李子柒成立四川子柒文化传播有限公司，杭州微念为该公司大股东，持股 51%，李子柒为第二大股东，持股 49%。目前杭州微念已完成 7 轮融资，投资方包括华映资本、新浪微博、芒果基金、字节跳动等。10 月 27 日传出消息，李子柒和微念纷争后数月后，股东字节跳动已于 10 月 16 日启动退出流程，投资不足半年。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-f02112ea4c2b606b8d2d67a021278d2e_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "166 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/495952970"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IhbjWwee7kehuEAMaCDcyNDkyNzE4ILam/4sGMAY4rwJAEnIJNDk1OTUyOTcweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "19_1635833342.8830345", "card_id": "Q_494974714", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 83}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "假以时日，生物可能演化出轮子吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-aa5d45a9e94788f0dbfedd7c124c2bf9_720w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "148 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/494974714"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IhbjWwee7kehuEAMaCDcyMjc1MzczIILb54sGMAM4+wFAE3IJNDk0OTc0NzE0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "20_1635833342.8835416", "card_id": "Q_495812923", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 100}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "网传华中师范大学监考老师顺走学生 iPad，校方回应「非本校老师，正在调查」，有什么信息值得关注？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "近日，一段疑似华中师范大学监考老师没收考生平板电脑，转卖时被学生当场撞见的视频在网络流传。 对此，华中师范大学官方微博 10 月 31 日发布通告称，网传「此电脑系监考老师在考场没收」与事实不符，现警方已介入。 网传武汉一高校监考老师没收学生东西后偷卖被当场抓获，校方：与事实不符 _ 腾讯新闻"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-2dd5acd31faaa1e58ebce1924b080e55_720w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "148 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/495812923"}}, "attached_info": "ClUIhbjWwee7kehuEAMaCDcyNDYxNDcxINGZ/YsGMAo48wNAFHIJNDk1ODEyOTI